  "keyFeatures": [
    "Interactive drag-and-drop task management",
    "Task dependencies with link types (S2S, S2E, E2S, E2E)",
    "Hierarchical tasks with summary/subtask support",
    "Configurable multi-row time scales with zoom support",
    "Customizable grid columns with inline editors",
    "Built-in toolbar, context menu, and modal editor",
    "Filtering (including natural language search)",
    "Localization with multiple locale support",
    "Light and dark themes (Material, Willow, WillowDark)",
    "Full TypeScript support",
    "RestDataProvider for server-side integration",
    "PRO edition with auto-scheduling, critical path, export, and more"
